    "# FERRUS ANIMUS — Pipeline de Correction et Retargeting\n",
    "**FREGATE 01 — Notebook Colab Principal**\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "IN/  ← FBX DeepMotion bruts\n",
    "  └─ INTEL  : analyse Claude + Gemini → plan_corrections.json\n",
    "  └─ EXEC   : 5 corrections (smooth, hips, foot, mask, camera)\n",
    "  └─ OUTPUT : retargeting → Roblox R15\n",
    "OUT/ ← FBX R15 corriges + rapport.json\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**Prerequis :**\n",
    "1. Google Drive monte (`/content/drive/MyDrive/FLOTTE-FERRUS/`)\n",
    "2. Blender 4.x binaire Linux dans `Drive/tools/blender-4.x-linux-x64/`\n",
    "3. Scripts FERRUS clones dans `Drive/FLOTTE-FERRUS/01_FERRUS_ANIMUS/codebase/`\n",
    "4. Secret Colab `AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY` configure (optionnel — fallback statique si absent)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n",
    "# [SETUP] Cellule 1 — Configuration\n",
    "# Adapter les chemins si votre structure Drive differe.\n",
    "# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "DRIVE_ROOT    = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/FLOTTE-FERRUS\"\n",
    "BLENDER_PATH  = f\"{DRIVE_ROOT}/tools/blender-4.x-linux-x64/blender\"\n",
    "SCRIPTS_ROOT  = f\"{DRIVE_ROOT}/01_FERRUS_ANIMUS/codebase\"\n",
    "INTEL_SCRIPTS = f\"{SCRIPTS_ROOT}/INTEL\"\n",
    "EXEC_SCRIPTS  = f\"{SCRIPTS_ROOT}/EXEC/operations\"\n",
    "OUT_SCRIPTS   = f\"{SCRIPTS_ROOT}/OUTPUT\"\n",
    "\n",
    "DIR_IN    = f\"{DRIVE_ROOT}/01_FERRUS_ANIMUS/IN\"\n",
    "DIR_OUT   = f\"{DRIVE_ROOT}/01_FERRUS_ANIMUS/OUT\"\n",
    "DIR_CACHE = \"/content/intel_cache\"\n",
    "DIR_TMP   = \"/content/ferrus_tmp\"\n",
    "\n",
    "for d in [DIR_OUT, DIR_CACHE, DIR_TMP]:\n",
    "    os.makedirs(d, exist_ok=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"[CONFIG] Chemins configures :\")\n",
    "print(f\"  Drive root  : {DRIVE_ROOT}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  Blender     : {BLENDER_PATH}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  IN          : {DIR_IN}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  OUT         : {DIR_OUT}\")\n"
   ]
